WEBVTT

00:08.073 --> 00:09.374
This week on "Vice,"

00:09.476 --> 00:12.267
the search for a cure for ALS.

00:13.313 --> 00:14.873
Robert Hebron:
<i>We're fighting the clock.</i>

00:14.948 --> 00:18.463
What I don't know is if there's
enough time for my daughter.

00:18.591 --> 00:21.459
How many people in the US
are getting your drug?

00:21.561 --> 00:22.660
In the US, nobody.

00:22.762 --> 00:24.662
The FDA is worried about safety.

00:24.764 --> 00:27.832
<i>Every day that passes,
he's losing more of himself.</i>

